                              </div>
                          </amp-lightbox>
                          <br>
                          <p class="justify">Select the entry "Notification" in the go1984 explorer. You can now enter one or several recipients (separated by semicolons) into the field E-mail address. Adjust the subject line if you wish. The variable "%cameraname%" is automatically replaced by the name of the camera triggering the alarm when an e-mail is sent. You have the option to set a rest period which must elapse between sending two e-mails, by clicking on the clock icon. Simply click on the clock icon and then set the rest period you want.</p>
                        </div>
